"**Subscriber Rules (Paid rules, real-time updates)**: Immediate access to "
"the most up-to-date rules without any delay. Available only to users with a "
"Snort Subscriber Rule Set subscription. Oinkcode is required to access these"
" rules."
msgstr ""
"**Regole per abbonati (regole a pagamento, aggiornamenti in tempo reale)**: "
